        "subject": "LU-14685 build: liblustreapi.so to main package",
        "message": "LU-14685 build: liblustreapi.so to main package\n\nLU-9215 accidentally moved liblustreapi.so symlink to\nthe development rpm package causing linked application\nstart failures:\n\nerror while loading shared libraries: liblustreapi.so:\ncannot open shared object file: No such file or directory\n\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9995\nChange-Id: Ie7be045ac2b7f781ef91d71fa518dc990410b79f\nFixes: 16af4e5 (\"LU-9215 build: Re-add the lustre-devel package\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Zarochentsev <alexander.zarochentsev@hpe.com>\n"
